org.sakaiproject.cheftool.menu

Class MenuEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sakaiproject.cheftool.menu.MenuEntry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MenuItem

    public class MenuEntry
extends Object
implements MenuItem

    MenuEntry is a clickable entry in a menu.
